Definition: near in time or place or relationship
Example: as the wedding day drew near; stood near the door; don't shoot until they come near; getting near to the true explanation; her mother is always near; The end draws nigh; the bullet didn't come close; don't get too close to the fire
Synonyms: nigh, close, in, time, or, place, relationship, as, the, wedding, day, drew, stood, door, don, t, shoot, until, they, come, getting, to, true, explanation, her, mother, is, always, The, end, draws, bullet, didn, get, too, fire
Category: adv.all
